OL,3,CJob losses as retailer to shut 13
OL,4,CWelsh stores
OL,6,FCarpetright has been bought in a
OL,7,Frescue deal by rival Tapi, but will
OL,8,Fshut 13 stores in Wales and another
OL,9,F200 across England, Scotland, and
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FMore than 1000 jobs will be lost in
OL,13,Fthe UK- with 54 in Wales.
OL,15,F41 people have already lost their jobs-
OL,16,F with a final 13 redundancies tomorrow.
