OL,3,CJob losses as retailer to shut 13
OL,4,CWelsh stores
OL,6,FIt was announced on Monday the
OL,7,Fflooring retailer Tapi had agreed to
OL,8,Fbuy 54 Carpetright stores, two
OL,9,Fwarehouses, the brand and its
OL,10,Fintellectual property in a pre-pack
OL,11,Fadministration deal.
OL,13,FHowever, the deal will not save the
OL,14,Fmajority of the business, the only
OL,15,FWelsh store included in the deal is in
OL,16,FCarmarthen.
OL,18,FHere is a full list of the Welsh
OL,19,Fstores expected to close over the
OL,20,Fcoming days, as provided by
OL,21,Fadministrators PwC:
