OL,6,F` Swansea ` Llansamlet
OL,8,FZelf Hussain, Joint Administrator for
OL,9,FPwC, said "Carpetright has fallen
OL,10,Fvictim to challenges facing many
OL,11,Fretailers, especially those selling
OL,12,Fbig ticket items.
OL,14,F"A mixture of factors, including a big
OL,15,Freduction in consumer spending due to
OL,16,Fcost of living pressures, lower home
OL,17,Fsales and a debilitating cyber attack
OL,18,Fmade it impossible for the business to
OL,19,Fcontinue in its current form.
